on This includes On-field independent observation and collection of data by the Survey Agency.Citizen Feedback is an essential component. People will be asked questions face to face or through outbound calls, 1969, Swachhta App, Swachh Manch and Swachh Surveskshan 2019 Portal.Swachh Survekshan 2019 will also focus separately on sanitation and garbage-free certifications by independent third party. Final Results and Winner City will be declared on the basis of scores attained by cities on these parameters.Swachh Survekshan 2019 \u2013 Complete DetailsThis Swachh Bharat Survey will be conducted across all cities and towns across the country between 4th to 31st January 2019. Swachh Survekshan will encourage large scale citizen participation and ensure sustainability of initiatives taken towards garbage free and open defecation free cities.Swachh Survekshan 2019 HighlightsThe important features and highlights of Swachh Survekshan 2019 are as follows:-World\u2019s largest cleanliness surveyAround 4237 cities coveredThe Swachhta Survey completed within 28 daysIt has GFC STAR RATING, ODF, ODF+ and ODF++ ratingsThis time it is a completely digitized and paperless surveyMore than 4.5 Lakh documents were uploaded by citiesTill date, there are 41 lakhs geotagged photos captured from fieldIn this survey, there is massive participation by citizensAround 64 Lakhs citizen feedback collectedThis time, the social media outreach is 4 croresSwachh Survekshan 2019 will provide credible outcomes and a 3rd party certification will validate this. All the existing systems will be institutionalized through online processes. This will create awareness among all sections of society and tell them the about the importance of working together in making towns and cities a better place to live in. Swachh Survekshan Logo will soon be released by MoHUA.This will increase the participation of general public in this Swachhta Mission. This survey will also promote healthy competition among towns and cities. These towns and cities would then be able to improve service delivery to citizens and will ensure cleaner cities for living.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: www.swachhmanch.in, www.swachhsurvekshan2019.org  at  "}